==H5N1==
{{H5N1}}
{{Main|H5N1}}

Influenza A virus subtype H5N1, also known as A(H5N1) or simply H5N1, is a subtype of the [[Influenzavirus A|Influenza A virus]] which can cause illness in humans and many other animal species.<ref name=ICTV46.0.1>

